Doctor_Name

Specialization

Phone_No

Department



2. Patient

Patient_ID (Primary Key)

Patient_Name

Age

Gender

Address

Phone_No



3. Appointment

Appointment_ID (Primary Key)

Patient_ID (Foreign Key)

Doctor_ID (Foreign Key)

Appointment_Date

Disease

Status



4. Treatment

Treatment_ID (Primary Key)

