---

Relationships:

Relationship	Description	Type

Doctor — Appointment	One doctor can have many appointments	1 : M
Patient — Appointment	One patient can have many appointments	1 : M
Patient — Treatment	One patient can have many treatments	1 : M
Treatment — Bill	One treatment generates one bill	1 : 1



